      <title>Cleanp 将在珠穆朗玛峰最高营地工作数年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-06/mount-everest-s-highest-camp-is-littered-with-frozen-garbage-and-cleanup-is-likely-to-take-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加德满都尼泊尔（美联社）——据一位夏尔巴人称，世界最高峰的最高营地上到处都是垃圾，需要几年时间才能清理干净，他带领着一支队伍清理了珠穆朗玛峰峰顶附近的垃圾并挖出了被冰冻多年的尸体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-06/mount-everest-s-highest-camp-is-littered-with-frozen-garbage-and-cleanup-is-likely-to-take-years</guid>
